1. Test class -> @isTest --> ClassNameTest
2. Test method -> @isTest
    -> call the method which we want to test.
    -> if data is required, then we prepare data and then we call our method.
    -> assert to verify if method is working as expected.
        a. Prepare data
        b1. test.startTest
        c. call method
        b2. test.stopTest
        d. assert
3. TestSetup -> @TestSetup
    -> prepare common data for entire test class.